	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-06-24T04:24:18">SDL PLC is a provider of an integrated cloud solution. The Company's digital experience includes a set of digital experience accelerators that allow the creation of Web and optimized e-commerce experiences. Its Knowledge center includes the creation of product knowledge views that offer an experience for documentation and self-service support. Customer analytics includes a single view of customer data, including profile, situational data, transactional data and third-party data. Language includes helping global brands in communicating across regions and languages. Its segments include the Language Services segment, which provides translation service for customer's multilingual content in multiple languages, and the Technology segment, which includes the sale of enterprise, desktop and statistical machine translation technologies, content management campaign management, social media monitoring and marketing analytic technologies together with associated consultancy and other services.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2015-08-09T22:11:33">BRIEF: For the six months ended 30 June 2015, SDL plc revenues increased 4% to L133.9M. Net income increased from L1.9M to L3.9M. Revenues reflect Language Services segment increase of 4% to L76.1M, Technology segment increase of 3% to L57.8M, Rest of the World segment increase of 34% to L20M, United States segment increase of 11% to L47.2M. Net income benefited from Net Foreign Exchange Losses increase from L100K to L3M (income).</Text>
	</TextInfo>
